{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the whole family went up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a little slight accident, you know, which happened, I mean, which was really nearly tragic.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, to-- to have for Pesach things, like fat and everything, we have to think when the goose season is on, right?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, the goose season, don't you make-- you prepare sort of a-- use-- use fat for the everyday life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But for Pesach, it's rare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because Pesach, you can't get it in our place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we've been moving, for somehow, some reason, somebody stole the canister of Pesach fat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Could you imagine my mother's face?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, what are we going to do during Pesach?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyhow, that has been solved, because in Budapest, you could buy anything--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] --kosher.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to Budapest and-- Do you-- can I just ask you?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did your father's brothers remain behind?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Father's brothers bring him and father's mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another family-- father's sister, which actually they were in Budapest before us, and the husband with the two girls, is still alive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were already in Budapest, so it was easy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was something which essential for us to move.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And secondly, we moved to a big place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And thirdly, we have sister and brother-in-law there, so sort of we just transplanted the family from Fil'akovo-- part of the family in Fil'akovo into Budapest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, financial-wise it wasn't so easy, because we still owed mortgage on the other house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- we sent this thing, and all this moving, and all this apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we could not live from the money which we had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We definitely had to earn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father tried to join non-Jewish businessmen, because you couldn't act on your own.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
